name: "The Scream" by Pablo Picasso [AI art]
description: This painting is a tribute to both Pablo Picasso and Edvard Munch.  What if “The Scream” was not painted by Edvard Munch, but by Picasso? How would it look? Our AI did have a go at it, trained on “La Muse” of Pablo Picasso and then it did repaint “The Scream”. Final cleanup was manually done in photoshop.  2200 x 2768
